description: Offer deadline May 28th at Noon. FIRST TIME HOMEBUYERS! Amazing opportunity for an updated one bedroom condo with assigned parking in South Boston. Kitchen has been updated recently with new appliances, countertops, and cabinets. Beautiful dark walnut hardwood floors. Great potential in the basement. First time homebuyer with income limits of 80% AMI of the HUD 2023 guidelines. If you earn less than $86,050 for one person and $98,350 for a household of two, you can purchase this wonderful property. City of Boston must approve the sale. The prospective buyer shall obtain a 30-year fixed rate mortgage loan conforming with the Fannie Mae guidelines with a Loan to Value (LTV) ratio of less than or equal to 97% of the maximum resale price.
